e monster's stolen ATK, STR, DEX, etc.</P><P>5) Wizards get anti-gate spells...give necros (or maybe mages) anti-summoning spells.</P><P>6) Group version of Vampiric Embrace.</P><P>Savan<BR>Afterlife</P><P></P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
